# AI Caller ID – Product Overview

## Mission
- Help users identify unknown phone numbers without calling back.
- Use an AI voice agent to collect identification and publish public number profiles.

## Success Criteria
- ≥80% of calls return a person or organization name.
- >1,000 organic searches per day within three months.
- Each lookup produces an SEO landing page with transcript + metadata.
- Users confirm ≥70% of identities as correct.

## Target Audiences
- Consumers who want quick caller insight with privacy preserved.
- Businesses that will later claim and maintain their listings.
- SEO visitors discovering profiles via search engines.

## Tone & Design Language
- “Personal detective” vibe: minimal, airy layouts with pastel accents.
- Feels smart and mysterious while staying approachable and privacy forward.

## Key Risks to Watch
- Consent and GDPR compliance for recording AI calls.
- Call duration must stay under one minute to control costs.
- Accuracy of name recognition (target ≥80%).
- Publication of transcripts must not expose sensitive data.
